    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269060/extras/8e5d6a01110659c99af7c5e971e956c0.avif?t=1762829754\" width=600 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uh-Oh</h2><br>Look where your inability to leave well enough alone has gotten us all. What started as an innocent day of general slacking, resistance collusion, and commercial espionage has somehow devolved into a cross dimensional odyssey with the lives of all your friends (and some of your foes) on the line!<br><br>In the mysterious depths of the videohole, reality is warped, memories are twisted, and the very nature of past events is obscured in literally the most inconvenient way possible. Cosmic gods (some malevolent even!) haunt and hamper your every attempt to save your dearest homies from their purgatorial fate. But you’re not gonna let that stop you, because you love them!<br><br>Right?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269060/extras/fcd1631955340f0d9d9ac38eb2d743e8.webp?t=1762829754\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set your feeble, retail-slacker will against a cosmic force that eludes comprehension.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel between worlds based on the cognitions of your friends, all with individual play styles and genres.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rage against your and your friends’ fading memories to connect their worlds to the mysterious videohole depths, and unlock more secrets within.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More like episode 2-5: Over 4x the length of episode 1.</li></ul>",
